  <div class='container-fluid py-5'>
    <div class='container py-5 mb-3'>
      <div class='row g-5'>
        <div class='col-lg-8'>
          <div class='img-destaque position-relative overflow-hidden'>
            <img class='img-fluid' src='../app/assets/img/posts/destaques/67_criatividade e inovação.png' alt='Imagem Destaque' />
          </div>
          <div class='content-blog position-relative overflow-hidden'>
            <div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Embora frequentemente associados, inova&ccedil;&atilde;o e criatividade n&atilde;o s&atilde;o </span><span class="NormalTextRun ContextualSpellingAndGrammarErrorV2Themed SCXW232008101 BCX8">sin&ocirc;nimos</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">. Enquanto a criatividade &eacute; a habilidade de conceber algo original ou incomum, a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o vai al&eacute;m, transformando novas ideias em resultados econ&ocirc;micos vi&aacute;veis. Ambas s&atilde;o essenciais para o sucesso no ambiente de trabalho: a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o depende da criatividade para pensar de forma disruptiva, enquanto a criatividade necessita da inova&ccedil;&atilde;o para ser implementada de maneira eficaz.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Shawn Hunter define criatividade em "Out </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW232008101 BCX8">Think</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">: </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW232008101 BCX8">How</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW232008101 BCX8">Innovative</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8"> Leaders Drive </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW232008101 BCX8">Exceptional</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW232008101 BCX8">Outcomes</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">" como a capacidade de gerar conceitos originais, um est&aacute;gio inicial onde as ideias come&ccedil;am a se materializar e os planos s&atilde;o desenvolvidos.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Por outro lado, Ernest </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW232008101 BCX8">Gundling</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">, em "The 3M Way </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW232008101 BCX8">to</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">Innovation</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">: </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW232008101 BCX8">Balancing</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8"> People </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW232008101 BCX8">and</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8"> Profit", descreve inova&ccedil;&atilde;o como a implementa&ccedil;&atilde;o bem-sucedida de novas ideias que geram benef&iacute;cios econ&ocirc;micos tang&iacute;veis. &Eacute; o processo de transformar inven&ccedil;&otilde;es em produtos comerciais.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>A criatividade &eacute; uma habilidade individual subjetiva, enquanto a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; um processo organizacional replic&aacute;vel. Compreender essas diferen&ccedil;as &eacute; fundamental para construir uma cultura empresarial que aproveite ao m&aacute;ximo o potencial criativo para desenvolver solu&ccedil;&otilde;es verdadeiramente inovadoras. Embora distintas, essas abordagens s&atilde;o complementares e devem ser estimuladas de maneira equilibrada.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Para estimular a criatividade da equipe, &eacute; necess&aacute;rio superar o que Roger von </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW232008101 BCX8">Oech</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8"> denomina em "Um Toc na Cuca: T&eacute;cnicas para Quem Quer Ter Mais Criatividade na Vida" como "bloqueios mentais". Estes s&atilde;o:</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="list" start="1">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="15" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&ldquo;A </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">r</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">esposta</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">c</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">erta</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&rdquo;</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">: Um h&aacute;bito que inibe a cria&ccedil;&atilde;o de novas ideias e a resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o de problemas. Von </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW232008101 BCX8">Oech</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8"> destaca que "nada &eacute; mais perigoso do que uma ideia quando ela &eacute; a &uacute;nica que voc&ecirc; tem". Para superar este bloqueio, ele sugere pensar em uma "segunda resposta certa" e formular perguntas para obter m&uacute;ltiplas respostas.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="list" start="2">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="15" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&ldquo;Isso </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">n</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&atilde;o </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">t</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">em </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">l</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&oacute;gica&rdquo;</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">: Na fase inicial do processo criativo, &eacute; crucial estimular pensamentos difusos e usar met&aacute;foras para facilitar a compreens&atilde;o de ideias complexas.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="list" start="3">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="15" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&ldquo;Siga as </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">n</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">ormas&rdquo;</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">: Questionar as normas estabelecidas &eacute; essencial para fomentar a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o. Von </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW232008101 BCX8">Oech</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8"> aconselha verificar periodicamente ideias e normas, evitando se apegar excessivamente a elas.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="list" start="4">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="15" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="4" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&ldquo;Seja </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">p</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">r&aacute;tico&rdquo;</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">: </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">Pessoas c</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">riativ</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">a</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">s precisam entrar no estado germinativo, explorar sua imagina&ccedil;&atilde;o e formular solu&ccedil;&otilde;es. Isso envolve n&atilde;o julgar ideias prematuramente e explorar novas quest&otilde;es com intelig&ecirc;ncia.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="list" start="5">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="15" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="5" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&ldquo;Evite </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">a</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">mbiguidades&rdquo;</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">: Embora a clareza seja importante, no est&aacute;gio inicial da criatividade, a ambiguidade pode ser &uacute;til para explorar diferentes perspectivas e solu&ccedil;&otilde;es.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="list" start="6">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="15" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="6" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&ldquo;&Eacute; </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">p</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">roibido </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">e</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">rrar&rdquo;</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">: Erros s&atilde;o oportunidades de aprendizado e inova&ccedil;&atilde;o. &Eacute; crucial usar erros como insights para novas ideias e fortalecer a capacidade da equipe de correr riscos calculados.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="list" start="7">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="15" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="7" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&ldquo;Brincar &eacute;</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">f</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">alta de </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">s</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">eriedade&rdquo;</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">: O divertimento pode ser um catalisador poderoso para novas ideias. Brincar com problemas e criar um ambiente de trabalho leve e descontra&iacute;do pode estimular a criatividade.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="list" start="8">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="15" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="8" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&ldquo;Isso </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">n</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&atilde;o </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&eacute; </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">da </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">m</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">inha </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&aacute;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">rea&rdquo;</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">: Ampliar horizontes e buscar ideias de diferentes &aacute;reas pode enriquecer o processo criativo. Desenvolver uma mentalidade de "ca&ccedil;ador de novas ideias" &eacute; essencial.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="list" start="9">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="15" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="9" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&ldquo;N&atilde;o </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">s</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">eja </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">t</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">olo&rdquo;</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">: &Eacute; importante desligar o "detector de tolices" e explorar ideias fora do convencional sem se deixar levar por conformismo ou pensamento grupal.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW232008101 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="list" start="10">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW232008101 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="15" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="10" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW232008101 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&ldquo;Eu </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">n</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">&atilde;o </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">s</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">ou </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">c</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">riativo(a)&rdquo;</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW232008101 BCX8">: Acreditar no potencial das pr&oacute;prias ideias, experimentar novas abordagens e confiar no processo s&atilde;o fundamentais para cultivar a criatividade pessoal.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW232008101 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
